{"thig9.1:0.1":"Therigatha 9.1 ","thig9.1:0.2":"Navakanipata ","thig9.1:0.3":"Vaddhamatutherigatha ","thig9.1:1.1":"“Ma su te vaddha lokamhi, ","thig9.1:1.2":"vanatho ahu kudacanam; ","thig9.1:1.3":"Ma puttaka punappunam, ","thig9.1:1.4":"ahu dukkhassa bhagima. ","thig9.1:2.1":"Sukhanhi vaddha munayo, ","thig9.1:2.2":"aneja chinnasamsaya; ","thig9.1:2.3":"Sitibhuta damappatta, ","thig9.1:2.4":"viharanti anasava. ","thig9.1:3.1":"Tehanucinnam isibhi, ","thig9.1:3.2":"maggam dassanapattiya; ","thig9.1:3.3":"Dukkhassantakiriyaya, ","thig9.1:3.4":"tvam vaddha anubruhaya”. ","thig9.1:4.1":"“Visaradava bhanasi, ","thig9.1:4.2":"etamattham janetti me; ","thig9.1:4.3":"Mannami nuna mamike, ","thig9.1:4.4":"vanatho te na vijjati”. ","thig9.1:5.1":"“Ye keci vaddha sankhara, ","thig9.1:5.2":"hina ukkatthamajjhima; ","thig9.1:5.3":"Anupi anumattopi, ","thig9.1:5.4":"vanatho me na vijjati. ","thig9.1:6.1":"Sabbe me asava khina, ","thig9.1:6.2":"appamattassa jhayato; ","thig9.1:6.3":"Tisso vijja anuppatta, ","thig9.1:6.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","thig9.1:7.1":"“Ularam vata me mata, ","thig9.1:7.2":"patodam samavassari; ","thig9.1:7.3":"Paramatthasanhita gatha, ","thig9.1:7.4":"yathapi anukampika. ","thig9.1:8.1":"Tassaham vacanam sutva, ","thig9.1:8.2":"anusitthim janettiya; ","thig9.1:8.3":"Dhammasamvegamapadim, ","thig9.1:8.4":"yogakkhemassa pattiya. ","thig9.1:9.1":"Soham padhanapahitatto, ","thig9.1:9.2":"rattindivamatandito; ","thig9.1:9.3":"Matara codito santo, ","thig9.1:9.4":"aphusim santimuttamam”. ","thig9.1:10.1":"… Vaddhamata theri …. ","thig9.1:11.1":"Navakanipato nitthito. "}